S.FORM: == kakiliman == Ca-ke-luy-pu "Ke-low-ay-su-ys a kamu, Zagreb(zǎːɡreb) , Ted-a kamu malumayay a nipangangan Agram, A-ke-la-mu, Swng -ya-li a kamu, Zágráb" nu Ke-low-ay-si-ya a angangan atu Ca-ke-luy-pu a kuwan nu saayaway a seybu mahiza sa u satabakiay hamin nu kanatal, caay sakuwan a tukay. Ca-ke-luy-pu tini i enal nu bay utu 122m "400 a depah", kitizaan tini i Ke-low-ay-si-ya a satip saamisanay a Mey-te-wi-te-nice-san-nan-pow, labu iza ku Sa-wa a sa'wac muculil. :Zagreb(zǎːɡreb) ；德語舊稱:Agram,阿格拉姆；匈牙利語:Zágráb) 122m(400英尺), . nilaculan 1094 a mihcaan i sawalianay a Ka-pu-tu-al kiwkay a sakuwan nu kitizaan, "Ca-ke-luy-pu" uyni a nganga maazih tu i likisi a cudad. i 1845 a mihcaan Yang-ke.Ka-maw-bu mala nu Ca-ke-luy-pu nu saayaway a kinciw. i 1945 a mihcaan kilul tu kakatuud nu tademaw atu malahad ku tukay, Ca-ke-luy-pu mala angangan tu nu Ke-low-ay-si-ya. Ca-ke-luy-pu i Ke-low-ay-si-ya pikawawan micidek ku ngangan "sakuwan tu tukay". makiwan makakilac tu 17 a kitizaan, hatu tini i kaisasaay a hekal nu bayu a diheb nu Sa-wa. Ca-ke-luy-pu nu Ke-low-ay-si-ya hamin nu kanatal, Si-ow atu Ti-cong-hay atu walian a timul Ow-co nu kahenulan a saculilan. Ca-ke-luy-pu iza henay pasayzaay nu zumaan a kanatal tu kanatalay a silamalay. labu nu tukay iza hena ku saculilan nu dingkiay a kazizeng. i kunng-yen c ac ay lasubu a mkihc aan hawsa, ayza u Ca-ke-luy-pu kitizaan nu tukuay u An-ta-tung-ni-ya "Andautonia" caca kasumamadanay a niyazu' nu Low-ma, tini ayzaay a S-ci-ta-al-ye-ow. "Ca-ke-luy-pu" a ngangan saayaway tahkal i 1094 a mihcaan tu nisulitan, tawya Ca-ke-luy-pu iza tusa ku kahenulan a kalcapuan. sawalianay a Ka-pu-al, u kitizaay nu tabakiay a kiwkay nu Ca-ke-luy-pu, angangan nu mikawaway tu nu kiwkay a kitizaan. satipay ku tabakiay tu Ke-la-tay-ce, angangan aenengan nu malukay atu misiwbayay. Ke-la-tay-c atu Ca-ke-luy-pu i 1851 a mihcaan mapapulung nu Ye-si-pu.ye-la-ci nu mikuwanay. malecad ye-la-ci cung-tu a putah u sapikining cinizaan a misanga' patizeng. i Nan-s-la-bu-se-huy cu-i lyan-pang-kung-he-kow a zidayan, Ca-ke-luy-pu sa u kahenulan amin nu kanatal kitizaan nu kezay atu hamin nu sakatus nu tabakiay a tukay. Ke-low-ay-si-ya i 1991 a mihcaan u binawlan ku misingkiway, musakamu Ca-ke-luy-pu mala u angangan a tukay. Ke-low-ay-si-ya a kusi hamin sanad i Ca-ke-luy-pu, pasumukin, nn dingkiay, pitenun, hwa-sye, misanga'ay tu sapayu, in-swa, bukulay, mikawaway izaw ku gingku, miliwkuay, pasiwbayay hatini. Ca-ke-luy-pu i 2004 a mihcaan tademaw palalecad kanatal a nisanga'an katukuh 23,730 ku kalisiw "o-ming palalecad 28,114 ku kalisiw". 2005 a mihcaan palalecad nayay ku pisakawawan pakala tu 8% pasentu, malatusa ku nayay ku pisakawawan nu kanatal.
